As she was about to enter she suddenly felt a hand on her behind. Quickly she turned round to see some punk guy, stoned and obviously heading towards a different kind of establishement, leering at her suggestively. She thought about killing him but quickly dismissed the thought. Why have a hamburger when you can dine on steak? Still she couldn't let him get away with such behaviour........<br>
